ack.title: ACKNOWLEDGMENTS
ack.p: This work was funded by The Research Council of Norway as part of the research project “Total utilization of raw materials in the supply chain for food with a bio-economical perspective (CYCLE)” ( http://cycleweb.no/) [225349/E40, 2013].
